{"tid":1431151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用垃圾桶做盾 RB 有無得諗？ 集思廣益","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T12:22:06.000Z","uid":216513,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6d208c47279f05e0c0d20ad7bd14f593bb3411d1","tid":1431151,"uid":216513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:25:34.000Z","msg":"借ac借ac借ac<br />\n<br />\n話說小弟就做垃圾相關行業既 <br />\n日日望住啲垃圾桶 其實諗左好耐拎啲垃圾桶<br />\n放前線封路加做盾得唔得？<br />\n因為垃圾桶啲膠都算硬 加上入面會有垃圾<br />\n點都可以頂一頂先既 好過拎浮板<br />\n想做路障又可以拎索帶索住<br />\n索住左之後啲狗又難剪<br />\n同埋佢有轆呀 有轆呀 要推都方便啲<br />\n<br />\n但係我驚有人嫌臭呀 污糟嗰啲<br />\n不過戴左豬嘴手套應該還好既<br />\n如果有TG 可以用細既桶裝水放落去<br />\n冚蓋 搞掂 <br />\n如果要整既話 兩桶兩桶前後放 再拎索帶<br />\n 如下圖<br />\n<br />\n第一次開Po Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G2Fwq8p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2Fwq8p.png&h=4307f10f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f913ddc967b467cda47a3b242b2265be40d2d4a9","tid":1431151,"uid":298077,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d6EWEZPO28Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd6EWEZPO28Q&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=ba9e4856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d6EWEZPO28Q</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48ea1beb102bbeeb5c7110d90ffddbf5bb1c868","tid":1431151,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:35:2